OL,5, An ex-employee of Donald Trump's has   
OL,6, admitted that he knew the former       
OL,7, president was inflating the size of his
OL,8, apartment in his signature Trump Tower.
OL,10,FAllen Weisselberg, the Trump           
OL,11,FOrganisation's former chief financial  
OL,12,Fofficer (CFO), made the admission at a 
OL,13,Fcivil trial in New York.               
OL,15,FHe said records overstated the size of 
OL,16,Fthe flat by some 20,000 sq feet.       
OL,18,FMr Trump is accused of inflating the   
OL,19,Fvalue of properties by more than $2bn  
OL,20,F(#1.6bn).                              
